{"type": "article", "id": 33393, "title": "这只优雅的小鹿，必要的时候还能变成一把钳子｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-17T23:05:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 21616, "name": "Bebop"}, {"id": 31533, "name": "iThinking"}, {"id": 34006, "name": "Teehee"}, {"id": 34007, "name": "TACS"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 186, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161017153801cQqyYn5wxKEC6WUP.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>LED Aluminum Light by BEBOP</h3><p>轻质的铝材搭配半透明的硅胶灯罩构成了韩国工作室 <a href=\"http://bebopdesigners.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BEBOP</a> 为 MUJI 设计的<a href=\"http://bebopdesigners.com/#/led-aluminum-light/\" rel=\"nofollow\">便携式灯具</a>，极简的造型体现了品牌本身的风格。可拆卸灯罩取下后安装在把手另一侧就让它从手电筒变为一盏手持灯，把手的平行横条纹则是考虑到抓握需求后特意设计的结果。目前这个灯具还处于概念设计阶段，并未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154014X2hO7A5ftHDKZE3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666935\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154014KnIvcboa2p8qW63N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666935\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154015iYIk6mcraQgOMElS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666935\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154014fmGYIj9goehQvAWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666935\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154015TAgQjw4OYBRI7sod.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666935\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154015nTs35XFf9ocuEKJH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666935\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dear Deer Pilers by iThinking</h3><p>曾推出过犀牛小锤子的台湾品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ithinking.com.tw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">iThinking</a> 继续着让工具变得更加有趣的尝试，最近它推出了一款名叫 Dear Deer 的摆设，鹿角的部分还可以用作钳子，优雅而吸睛。它有黑白两种颜色以及定制版可选，无论是慵懒的卧鹿还是自信的立鹿，都能够营造出轻松温馨的氛围。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1538570791/dear-deer-the-incarnation-of-elegance\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 33 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154056heMfcXoU9kbYst83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154056XiUzR0GsYd2vJIOq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610171540574fZMpkueVQ0WEmvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610294\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154057G0coLQujA4zFsMaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154057AVSgnhi7HzLpJfx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154056xn0X4GIB71fLu2am.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Illa &amp; Illeta crib by Teehee</h3><p>越来越多的设计师和品牌在为孩子设计家具时更倾向于模块化的设计，对总是有着好奇心的小朋友来说，一个既让他们感到熟悉并且能提供活动空间的环境更符合他们的日常需求。荷兰家具品牌 <a href=\"https://www.teehee.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Teehee</a> 为此专门设计了能陪伴小朋友们成长的 <a href=\"https://www.teehee.eu/product/illa-lacquered-finish/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Illa</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.teehee.eu/product/illeta/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Illeta</a> 两款家具，孩子长大后婴儿床的高度可以调低，变成一张沙发床。除此之外，家具还附有储物柜和一个安装在顶部的衣架，这些能够根据情况进行调整的功能分区也免去了家长们常换家具的苦恼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101715414615GEIcw9ZjpzYoh3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154146eRDV1spOo3XY2Ti5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154147YfCL4BQD9HzwbEZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154147wrqOmvyKBY3GhMWS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154147sFQPUmbNEZzTj3dy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154147A6dBcQSx8Pn5GKvM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Automatic Vintage Lens watch by TACS</h3><p>日本腕表品牌 <a href=\"http://www.tacs-image.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TACS</a> 的创始人 Yoshiaki Motegi 一直都坚持简约的设计原则，从生活细节中汲取灵感融入到腕表的设计当中，最近他带领设计团队打造了一款或许会让摄影爱好者心动的复古镜头表。如果说相机的魔法都发生在正中央的话，那么表面中间暴露的构造则会让你感受到机械表的神奇。表面上的玻璃罩微微鼓起，不仅模仿了鱼眼镜头的感觉，也让时间显得更大了一点。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1777279053/tacs-automatic-vintage-lens\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 425 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154202a2vVXARSt9GZJL5H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610171542014YhNzdDRtjbfX8ep.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154201RJX1mxrowVTuLYbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154201nCaePFvXEs5ucrDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.344118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610171542023LRpQqFuefivkWoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.010294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017154201rXxBfPgQYdnvm57w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Ding by Ding Labs</h3><p>          </p><p>错过快递员门铃或是因为专心做事没有听到铃声的经历相信在不少人身上都发生过，为了让开门迎客这件事变得更加方便，来自伦敦的设计团队带来了一款名叫 <a href=\"http://dingproducts.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ding</a> 的智能门铃。它由安放在门口的门铃（Button）和配对的扬声器（Chime）两个设备组成，还有一个专用的应用。一旦有人按下门铃，提示器就会发出响声，如果你不在家或者不方便出去开门，就可以通过手机与对方交流。作为一款智能设备，Ding 不仅能自定义铃声还提供了免打扰模式。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dingproducts/ding-a-beautifully-simple-smart-doorbell\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 129 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017170614iHw02RcWtUIAEJez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.595588\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017170614R6bDIdpOzUuTgrsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.076471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017170614MK5grtykjCoTh9ER.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.016176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017170614uv3ZK94DMNPldqne.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017170614jUDf9CiwAsedmlQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.544118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>FUSE by Devendran Draguian</h3><p>          </p><p>印度设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Draguian\" rel=\"nofollow\">Devendran Draguian</a> 以新旧之间的差异和融合为主题设计了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43765001/FUSE\" rel=\"nofollow\">FUSE</a> 的椅子。为了呈现出时间流逝后的粗糙感，Draguian 选择了木料和不锈钢两种材质，用一种独特的结构把两者组合在一起：座椅的两条前腿与扶手成一体，插入了不锈钢座位前的缺口，但扶手本身并没有继续延伸和椅背连接在一起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017182118UO6TVrsqdux0DyL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610171821189ajWsRGeIgDAmpfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017182118WeM4VU52b9gjN6p1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017182118MNcjGCb8TzAWxqV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161017182118dkaNtp8GCreFIy2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}